Package: jolicloud-iso
Architecture: any
Depends: ${jolicloud-iso:Depends}
Recommends: ${jolicloud-iso:Recommends}
Breaks: ${jolicloud-iso:Breaks}
Description: The Jolicloud ISO template
 This package depends on all of the original packages used to create a
 Jolicloud ISO image.
 .
 This package will be automatically removed after installing Jolicloud from
 an ISO, and does not need to be manually installed to an existing system
 by the end-user.

